One big cause of vaccum can failure is gas getting to the flexable diaphram.? Must have the proper loop in the vaccum line to prevent this.
You can see the one of several of?the type of loops VW used over the years in this image just to the left of the carb.
http://www.thesamba.com/vw/archives/manuals/aug65bus/page46.jpg
